$ Excel: Data -> Sort & Filter -> Advanced

{ Actions

  There are two action possibilities:
    • Filter the list, in place
    • Copy to another place

  These two actions correspond to the two values of the → https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/office/vba/api/excel.xlfilteraction[`xlFilterAction`] enumeration:
    • `xlFilterCopy`
    • `xlFilterInPlace`

}
{ VBA

  The functionality of advanced sort & filter is exposed through a → Microsoft/Office/Excel/Object-Model/Range/advancedFilter[range's `advancedFilter`] method.

}

sa:
  
  The → Microsoft/Office/Excel/functions/filter[worksheet function `Filter`] offers a similar functionality.
